                "invention-title": [
                    "System and method for converting methane into high-purity hydrogen and carbon material",
                    "一种甲烷转化为高纯氢气与碳材料的系统和方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a scheme for converting methane into high-purity hydrogen and a carbon material, which comprises the following steps: removing water and oxygen in methane gas through a purification device, introducing the methane gas into a liquid molten metal conversion device, and directly cracking to obtain a carbon material 1 and hydrogen; further cracking through a gas-phase relay conversion device to obtain a carbon material 2 and hydrogen; introducing the generated mixed gas into a volatile metal recovery device, and cooling metal catalyst steam in the volatile metal recovery device to obtain metal catalyst particles; then introducing the residual mixed gas into a pressure swing adsorption device for separation to obtain hydrogen; and then the residual methane gas is introduced into the volatile metal recovery device to be cooled, and the residual methane gas carries condensed metal catalyst particles to return to the liquid molten metal conversion device to be recycled. According to the scheme, the methane gas and the metal catalyst are fully recycled, the methane can be converted into the carbon material and the high-purity hydrogen to the greatest extent, no metal catalyst is lost in the whole process, and the method has the advantages of continuity and low cost."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供一种将甲烷转化为高纯氢气与碳材料的方案，通过净化装置去除甲烷气体中的水和氧后，将其通入液态熔融金属转化装置，直接裂解得到碳材料1和氢气；再经过气相接力转化装置进一步裂解，得到碳材料2和氢气；将生成的混合气体通入挥发金属回收装置，冷却其中的金属催化剂蒸气，得到金属催化剂颗粒；然后将剩余混合气体通入变压吸附装置进行分离，得到氢气；再将剩余甲烷气体通入挥发金属回收装置，对其进行降温，并携带冷凝的金属催化剂颗粒返回液态熔融金属转化装置，循环使用。该方案实现了对甲烷气体和金属催化剂的充分回用，能将甲烷最大限度地转化为碳材料和高纯氢气，整个过程完全没有金属催化剂损失，具有连续化且低成本的优势。"
                }
            ]
